dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning in Langlade County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Langlade_Zoning_2016.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Farmland', 'Floodplain', and 'General'. [This layer represents farmland preservation areas in Langlade County, Wisconsin referenced to the Wisconsin Transverse Mercator System (WTM) GCS_North_American_1983_HARN.]
